InventoryEOQandReorderCalculation is a BusinessTask
    owned by ic

    Patterns
        implements ManualTransaction
        implements StaticJava
            Reports
                InventoryEOQandReorderCalculationReport

    Parameters
        Company                 is an InventoryCompany
        Location                is an InventoryLocation
        ReportGrp               is an InventoryReportGroup
        NbrPdsHistory           is Numeric size 2
        TransfersOpt            is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                Yes value is "Y"
                No  value is "N"
        AdjustmentsOpt          is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                Yes value is "Y"
                No  value is "N"
        NbrPdsForecast          is Numeric size 2
        SelAllPtCds             is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                Yes value is "Y"
                No  value is "N"
        UpdateReoPt             is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                Yes value is "Y"
                No  value is "N"
        SelAllQtyCds            is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                Yes value is "Y"
                No  value is "N"
        UpdateEoq               is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                Yes value is "Y"
                No  value is "N"
        UpdateReoQty            is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                Yes value is "Y"
                No  value is "N"
        Variance                is Decimal size 4.1
        RoundingOption          is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                Yes value is "Y"
                No  value is "N"
        InvenMajcl              is a MajorInventoryClass
        InvenMincl              is a MinorInventoryClass
        IncludeInactive         is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                Yes value is "Y"
                No  value is "N"
        ItemSelection           is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                AllItems           value is blank
                InventoryItemsOnly value is "I"
                NonStockItemsOnly  value is "N"
                    default label is "Non-Stock Items Only"

